<dl class="lemma-reference collapse nslog-area log-set-param" data-nslog-type="2" log-set-param="ext_reference">
<dt class="reference-title">参考资料</dt>
<dd class="reference-list-wrap">
<ul class="reference-list">
<li class="reference-item reference-item--type1 " id="reference-[1]-899-wrap">
<span class="index">1.</span>
<a class="gotop anchor"  name="refIndex_1_899" id="refIndex_1_899" title="向上跳转" href="#ref_[1]_899">&nbsp;&nbsp;</a>
<a rel="nofollow" href="/reference/100571/2276cUtlzl-Hj_rDpoS87D8gUsL2a1N1qoMp5NtjkX29wwBmRMoDQkdt7v3V66Bx2HTJaNpvz_GS1dlQaIhmAV_eXMiPJd0G4ohx-GqmA-_tgT_wH84I-dO2mCa6OJmtqtG2tC8qYZetizY" target="_blank" class="text">服务器网络安全分析与研究<span class="linkout">&nbsp;</span></a>
